<br>
I'm really looking forward to getting this. Can't wait to charm a griff and go pay Mr. Broon a visit.... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Similar questions for mezzing.  I've been doing a lot of crowd control lately (8 Sarnaks of various types at once - shudder) and while I think I've got the basic tactic down, would appreciate hearing about your experiences.<br>
<br>
For what it's worth, my base charisma is 95, and I've been experimenting with the difference between using my instrument and a Koad'dal Blood Doll which raises it to 98.  So far I'm not sure which is working better...  <br>
<br>
Amerygn<br>
