<br>
As for mezzing, I don't normally play crowd control in groups because I'm usually soloing. And if I get a multi-pull, I just fear everything and chain the mob I want to kill (I am OBSESSED with fear kiting). Since I usually hunt in Kunark, fearing will push the mob far away enough that I'll never see it again. I find it works much better than mezzing it (because this doesn't really need to be refreshed).<br>
<br>
Good luck with your hunts Amerygn. Let me in on any bardic secrets you may unveil, I'm always looking for insight on our class. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><BR>
