<br>
Also when I charm I have use it as a pet and let it attack while I can sing other songs for the 15 or so seconds that it is my pet.  When everyone is done fighting a big mob I usually charm the monster one last time so ppl can heal and figure out if they need to back up or not <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
<br>
Now about mezzing <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  I usually use mezzing in every fight becuase it lessens the about of times they can hit your tank <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  or anyone else for that matter.  I can also twist the mezz with other things so the group usually is unaware that I do this.<br>
<br>
